title: Easy Street Draw 2.0
description:
Easy Street Draw is a drawing tool designed to address the specialized drawing requirements of crash diagramming. The Easy Street Draw software provides shapes and tools that enable the rapid creation of accurate crash scene drawings. Easy Street Draw uses measurement units, concepts and terms familiar to the officer in the field. The result is a software system that provides the drawing power to represent any collision scene, yet is very easy to learn and use.

Copy the Trancite File to your computer's Program Files folder. Copy the item located in the Windows folder into your computer's windows folder. Open the Trancite File, find the Intersection icon, Right click and create a shortcut on the desktop. Open the program from the desktop and You should be up and running! Enjoy.
